Lvl. 89 Beast Boss
35 health
45 attack
50 defense
-20 attack against player or team holding 3 rotten apples
Lormus, son of the DragonKing, Kairus, is an evil dragon who tortures the souls of the dungeon. He is known as the "Souleater". Losing to him results in irreversible annihilation with no ability to be resurrected.
After killing,
Roll 4D6 > 18 for 3 chest items
